==List of existing Mozart compositions== To maintain as much of the original K-numbering of the list as possible, while re-ordering in the revised, chronological sequence, letters were added to the new numbers. The following list shows Köchel's original designation (K{{sup|1}}) and the sixth edition (K{{sup|6}}). Other addenda and supplements to the catalogue are marked ''{{linktext|Anhang}}.'' (This has been abbreviated to 'Anh.' in the list below.) Works listed as composed for piano were most likely performed on harpsichord or piano (more properly, forte-piano), as the harpsichord was still current in Mozart's day.
